Package backend.data

Class CalculatorData

java.lang.Object
backend.data.CalculatorData
public class CalculatorData
extends java.lang.Object
CalculatorData contains Gedmatch calculator data (breakdown / color scheme). App supports 4 Gedmatch calculators.
